.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# ── WAW generated artifacts (managed by /waw-init; do not commit) ──
.claude/waw/runs/
.claude/waw/archive/
.claude/waw/state.json
.claude/waw/*.local.*
# Committed (do NOT ignore): workflow.json, project-notes.md, knowledge-graph.json, workflows/
